{"tid":1944870,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"(軍火)留意到連登仔係某個時候都幾信黑警講野","createTime":"2020-03-26T16:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T06:04:36.000Z","uid":33904,"like":156,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"984534df113ed722d8af403c837a14d326fe9efd","tid":1944870,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:29:56.000Z","msg":"次次黑警話搵到軍火，<br />\n都唔比人屌狗嫁禍，<br />\n狗話搵到咩就係咩，<br />\n唔係就係割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後個post就會變成，<br />\n係咪割 vs d狗又屈人<br />\n<br />\n咁當然而家呢刻唔會有人知係真係軍火斷正，定被狗插贓嫁禍，根據我地兩種應對，會有四個可能性。<br />\n<br />\n1. 手足真係有軍火被斷正，而我地信黑警真係冇嫁禍<br />\n<br />\n2. 手足真係有軍火被斷正，但我地老屈係黑警插贓<br />\n<br />\n3. 手足冇軍火，但我地錯信黑警既插贓<br />\n<br />\n4. 手足冇軍火，而我地認為係黑警老屈<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n每次有人被拉有軍火，<br />\n認為一定要接受真係有軍火既，<br />\n都係以：擴大使用軍火接受程度同防止日後使用會被捉鬼為論點，<br />\n但事實上話係d狗嫁禍，唔代表唔接受手足可以有軍火，亦唔代表日後見到有手足拎槍會捉佢鬼。<br />\n<br />\n其實只要表明：就算第時真係有人開槍都唔會割、唔會捉鬼，<br />\n屌狗插贓呢樣野，<br />\n唔理佢地有冇都好插贓都好，<br />\n都係冇損失。<br />\n<br />\n我希望以後係軍火新聞post入面大家會留呢句：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可以射死d狗緊係好，不過我懷疑係d狗插贓</span><br />\n<br />\n呢句野應該可以係以上四個情景下都拎到最佳效果"},{"pid":"2493fbc0011f10ac15d16aad5cd7f1eb56f4f180","tid":1944870,"uid":67896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:34:10.000Z","msg":"終於有理性分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaafa5d5804c8c4f6cc0f81d8314bfa3a2927264","tid":1944870,"uid":283912,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:40:02.000Z","msg":"Agger,幾時開始狗講咩我地都要硬食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係真嘅都唔會割,但都要prove到係真先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18af593f97e4c49e0950190e5e2c07872cce458a","tid":1944870,"uid":33904,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"eaafa5d5804c8c4f6cc0f81d8314bfa3a2927264","tid":1944870,"uid":283912,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:40:02.000Z","msg":"Agger,幾時開始狗講咩我地都要硬食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係真嘅都唔會割,但都要prove到係真先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:42:57.000Z","msg":"其他時間明明冇人信狗，<br />\n但次次一有軍火庫，<br />\n個個信到d狗十足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8cea99a48a0f382ebf065a34cb8df31daa174c","tid":1944870,"uid":35205,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"捉軍火唔著避彈衣<br />\n一係有人想狗死<br />\n一係就係一開始就知無軍火"},{"pid":"154fbf5b0f3b0f6f5983d28c60b9aa177077c917","tid":1944870,"uid":5523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"aa8cea99a48a0f382ebf065a34cb8df31daa174c","tid":1944870,"uid":35205,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"捉軍火唔著避彈衣<br />\n一係有人想狗死<br />\n一係就係一開始就知無軍火"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T21:17:52.000Z","msg":"又有道理"},{"pid":"6b13cc471ca8c60b6bf6f97d9c12635f975f6943","tid":1944870,"uid":95519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T21:25:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d87e16f1f6ad2e2c73c4d8bf01fe1c14023ef93c","tid":1944870,"uid":72749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa8cea99a48a0f382ebf065a34cb8df31daa174c","tid":1944870,"uid":35205,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"捉軍火唔著避彈衣<br />\n一係有人想狗死<br />\n一係就係一開始就知無軍火"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T21:29:08.000Z","msg":"突破瞎點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671f09595af9f8bcb19e87a8287c9c31179effc4","tid":1944870,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa8cea99a48a0f382ebf065a34cb8df31daa174c","tid":1944870,"uid":35205,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"捉軍火唔著避彈衣<br />\n一係有人想狗死<br />\n一係就係一開始就知無軍火"},"ci